docs.title: Access the lab environment

docs.text: Accessing lab environment Go to the Attendee Lab URL from the Workshop Labs menu item, From the Workshop Labs menu item, select the Lab Environment URL for the specific lab(s) you want to run Enter the workshop password: and click the Submit password button Click the Published Services URL to your environment. Note: The Published Service provides direct access to the VM environment that is used for all of the labs in the workshop. Select vnc.html from the directory listing page. Click Connect on the noVNC connection page Enter the noVNC password as passw0rd (That is a numeric zero in passw0rd) Follow the lab guide for instructions Note: Each lab guide includes the information for acessing the VM, how to login to the VM, login credentials, etc.
